To meet...

27:44.834 --> 27:51.824
Of course, as youngsters, your goals are set out 
for you by your parents if they're doing their job,

27:44.834 --> 27:51.824
and mine were. But when you take off for 
university, then you're on your own. You've got to

27:55.048 --> 27:58.413
make your own objectives and thereafter. Of 
course, this is during the New Deal, Franklin

28:00.215 --> 28:08.888
Roosevelt, so I was wondering what political 
persuasion your father was and what one you came to

28:00.215 --> 28:08.888
accept. My father was a very loyal Democrat. Of 
course, in those days, Republicans were still

28:13.172 --> 28:20.940
carpetbaggers.

